<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.1.8">
<l>mēlāt tēvarkaḷu nilattēvaru mēvittoḻu</l>
<l>mālār vantiṉanā ḷaṭiyēṉmaṉattē maṉṉiṉār</l>
<l>cēlēy kaṇṇiyarum peruñcelvamu naṉmakkaḷu</l>
<l>mēlāt tāytantaiyu mavarēyiṉi yāvārē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Māl, for whom the gods that are above come to earth, who them affectionately</l>
<l>worship, has come on one such day  into the heart of me, [his] servant, [and] stays.</l>
<l>Now [to me] he has become mother and father who are above</l>
<l>women with carp-like eyes, great wealth and good people.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
